column2: select astar.ra, astar.dec, #*(astar.ra - ap.racen)/cos(ap.deccen*PI()/#) as xfocal, #*ap.deccen*(astar.dec - ap.deccen) as yfocal, astar.ra - ap.racen as delta_ra, astar.dec - ap.deccen as delta_dec from apogeestar as astar join apogeePlate as ap on ap.location_id=astar.location_id where ap.plate = #
